'''ROUTE 66 Geographic Information Systems B.V.''' is a privately held company headquartered in Pfäffikon, Switzerland. ROUTE 66 was founded in 1992 and specializes in [[Navigation system|navigation]] software and hardware products.<ref name="company info">[https://web.archive.org/web/20140311122037/http://www.66.com/US/about/about-us/] </ref>

In 1999 the company opened a software development center in [[Brașov]], [[Romania]]. In 2005 the company moved all its research and development operations to the aforementioned location, which at that date employed 45 of the company's total of 65 employees.<ref>Adrian Nuta (5 Oct 2005) [http://www.wall-street.ro/articol/IT-C-Tehnologie/7019/Route-66-face-harti-digitale-la-Brasov.html Route 66 face harti digitale la Brasov], Wallstreet.ro</ref> In 2008, the company announced 2.4 million euros in revenue.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://incomemagazine.ro/articles/route-66-am-angajat-doar-20-de-oameni-din-cei-150-planificati|title=Route 66: Am angajat doar 20 de oameni din cei 150 planificati|website=Incomemagazine.ro|accessdate=22 August 2017}}</ref> In 2010, the company had 92 employees, of which 65 were software developers.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.realitatea.net/navigatie-gps-catre-salarii-de-3-000-de-euro-piscina-si-sala-de-fitness_710686.html|title=REALITATEA .NET|website=Realitatea.net|accessdate=22 August 2017}}</ref> In November 2013, ROUTE 66 launched their latest app  Navigate 6.  <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pocketgpsworld.com/ROUTE-66-launches-their-latest-navigation-app-2459.php|title=ROUTE 66 launches their latest navigation app|last=Team|first=PocketGPSWorld|website=PocketGPSWorld.com|access-date=2018-05-16}}</ref>

